SELECT
    IF(${test_path:json} = "", "Root", ${test_path:json}) AS node_title,
    IF(${test_path:json} = "", "", "â®Œ Parent") AS node_parent_title,
    IF(
        STRPOS(${test_path:json}, ".") = 0,
        "",
        LEFT(${test_path:json}, CHARACTER_LENGTH(${test_path:json}) - STRPOS(REVERSE(${test_path:json}), "."))
    ) AS node_parent_path,
    IF(${test_path:json} = "", "", "â®Œ Root") AS node_root_title,

    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param

SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    builds.architecture AS architecture,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests_num,
    MAX((CASE tests.status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
        (CASE tests.waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS tests_status_num
FROM ${dataset}.builds AS builds
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.tests AS tests
    ON
        tests.build_id = builds.id AND
        tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
        tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
        tests.path IS NOT NULL AND
        (${test_path:json} = "" OR
         tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
         STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
WHERE
    IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
    IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
GROUP BY
    builds.architecture
ORDER BY
    tests_status_num DESC,
    tests_num DESC,
    builds.architecture ASC

WITH intervals AS (
    SELECT
        interval_start,
        TIMESTAMP_ADD(interval_start, INTERVAL $__interval_ms*50 MILLISECOND) AS interval_end
    FROM UNNEST(
        GENERATE_TIMESTAMP_ARRAY(TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from),
                                 TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to),
                                 INTERVAL $__interval_ms*50 MILLISECOND)
    ) AS interval_start
)
SELECT
    interval_start AS time,
    IFNULL(tests.status, "UNKNOWN") AS metric,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests
FROM
    ${dataset}.builds AS builds, ${dataset}.tests AS tests
INNER JOIN
    intervals
    ON tests.start_time >= interval_start AND tests.start_time < interval_end
WHERE
    builds.id = tests.build_id AND
    IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
    IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE) AND
    tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
    (${test_path:json} = "" AND tests.path IS NOT NULL OR
     tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
     STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
GROUP BY
    time, metric
ORDER BY
    time ASC, metric ASC

/* Massage */
SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    origins,
    path,
    IF(${test_path:json} = "", path, SUBSTR(path, CHARACTER_LENGTH(${test_path:json}) + 2)) AS name,
    architectures,
    tests,
    status_num
FROM (
    /* Aggregate */
    SELECT
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT origin, ", ") AS origins,
        LEFT(base_prefix, CHAR_LENGTH(base_prefix) - 1) AS path,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT architecture, ", ") AS architectures,
        COUNT(DISTINCT id) AS tests,
        MAX((CASE status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
            (CASE waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS status_num
    FROM (
        /* Filter tests and extract path prefixes */
        SELECT
            tests.origin,
            tests.id,
            /* Prefix one level deeper than the displayed test's path */
            IFNULL(
                NULLIF(
                    /*
                     * Cut the test path up to and including the first dot
                     * after the currently-displayed test's path
                     */
                    LEFT(
                        tests.path,
                        INSTR(tests.path, ".", CHARACTER_LENGTH(${test_path:json}) + 2)
                    ),
                    ""
                ),
                tests.path || "."
            ) AS base_prefix,
            builds.architecture,
            tests.status AS status,
            tests.waived AS waived
        FROM ${dataset}.tests
        INNER JOIN
            ${dataset}.builds AS builds
            ON
                tests.build_id = builds.id AND
                IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
                IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
        WHERE
            tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
            tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
            tests.path IS NOT NULL AND
            (${test_path:json} = "" OR STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
    )
    GROUP BY
        base_prefix
)
ORDER BY
    name ASC

SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    checkouts.git_repository_url AS git_repository_url,
    checkouts.git_repository_branch AS git_repository_branch,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT builds.architecture, ", ") AS architectures,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests_count,
    MAX((CASE tests.status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
        (CASE tests.waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS tests_status_num
FROM
    ${dataset}.checkouts AS checkouts
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.builds AS builds
    ON
        checkouts.id = builds.checkout_id AND
        IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
        IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.tests AS tests
    ON
        builds.id = tests.build_id AND
        tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
        tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
        (${test_path:json} = "" AND tests.path IS NOT NULL OR
         tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
         STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
WHERE
    git_repository_url IS NOT NULL AND
    git_repository_branch IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    git_repository_url,
    git_repository_branch
ORDER BY
    tests_status_num DESC,
    tests_count DESC,
    git_repository_url ASC,
    git_repository_branch ASC

/*
 * Truncate a string with an ellipsis at speÑified length.
 */
CREATE TEMP FUNCTION TRUNCATE(str STRING, len INT64)
    RETURNS STRING
    AS (IF(len = 0 OR CHAR_LENGTH(str) <= len,
           str,
           CONCAT(SUBSTR(str, 1, len - 1), "â€¦")
       ));

/*
 * Replace NULL or empty string with a non-breaking space,
 * truncate anything else with ellipsis, if necessary.
 */
CREATE TEMP FUNCTION BLANK_OR_TRUNCATE(str STRING, len INT64)
    RETURNS STRING
    AS (IF(str IS NULL OR str = "", "Â ", TRUNCATE(str, len)));

/*
 * Format an array of strings as a three-line text with ellipsis
 */
CREATE TEMP FUNCTION ARRAY_TO_TEXT(strs ARRAY<STRING>, width INT64)
    RETURNS STRING
    AS (ARRAY_TO_STRING(
        [
            BLANK_OR_TRUNCATE(strs[SAFE_OFFSET(0)], width),
            BLANK_OR_TRUNCATE(strs[SAFE_OFFSET(1)], width),
            IF(ARRAY_LENGTH(strs) > 3, "â€¦",
               BLANK_OR_TRUNCATE(strs[SAFE_OFFSET(2)], width))
        ],
        "\n"
    ));

WITH
    revision_sources AS (
        SELECT
            git_commit_hash,
            patchset_hash,
            ARRAY_TO_TEXT(
                ARRAY_AGG(git_repository_url_str
                          ORDER BY rank DESC, git_repository_url_str,
                                   git_repository_branch_str, git_commit_name_str),
                128
            ) AS git_repository_urls_text,
            ARRAY_TO_TEXT(
                ARRAY_AGG(git_repository_branch_str
                          ORDER BY rank DESC, git_repository_url_str,
                                   git_repository_branch_str, git_commit_name_str),
                32
            ) AS git_repository_branches_text,
            ARRAY_TO_TEXT(
                ARRAY_AGG(git_commit_name_str
                          ORDER BY rank DESC, git_repository_url_str,
                                   git_repository_branch_str, git_commit_name_str),
                32
            ) AS git_commit_names_text,
        FROM (
            SELECT
                git_commit_hash,
                patchset_hash,
                git_repository_url_str,
                git_repository_branch_str,
                git_commit_name_str,
                IF(git_repository_url_str = "", 0, 4) +
                    IF(git_repository_branch_str = "", 0, 2) +
                    IF(git_commit_name_str = "", 0, 1) AS rank
            FROM (
                SELECT DISTINCT
                    git_commit_hash,
                    patchset_hash,
                    IFNULL(git_repository_url, "") AS git_repository_url_str,
                    IFNULL(git_repository_branch, "") AS git_repository_branch_str,
                    IFNULL(git_commit_name, "") AS git_commit_name_str,
                FROM
                    ${dataset}.checkouts AS checkouts
            )
        )
        GROUP BY
            git_commit_hash,
            patchset_hash
    )
/* Massage and join with sources */
SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    revisions.git_commit_hash,
    revisions.patchset_hash,
    origins_str,
    SUBSTR(revisions.git_commit_hash, 0, 12) AS git_commit_hash_short,
    revision_sources.git_repository_urls_text,
    revision_sources.git_repository_branches_text,
    revision_sources.git_commit_names_text,
    SUBSTR(revisions.patchset_hash, 0, 12) AS patchset_hash_short,
    IFNULL(CAST(checkouts_start_time AS STRING), "") AS checkouts_start_time_str,
    tests_num,
    tests_status_num
FROM (
    SELECT
        checkouts.git_commit_hash,
        checkouts.patchset_hash,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT checkouts.origin, ", ") AS origins_str,
        MIN(checkouts.start_time) AS checkouts_start_time,
        COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests_num,
        MAX((CASE tests.status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
            (CASE tests.waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS tests_status_num
    FROM
        ${dataset}.checkouts AS checkouts
    INNER JOIN
        ${dataset}.builds AS builds
        ON
            builds.checkout_id = checkouts.id AND
            IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
            IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
    INNER JOIN
        ${dataset}.tests AS tests
        ON
            tests.build_id = builds.id AND
            tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
            tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
            tests.path IS NOT NULL AND
            (${test_path:json} = "" OR
             tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
             STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
    GROUP BY
        checkouts.git_commit_hash,
        checkouts.patchset_hash
) AS revisions
INNER JOIN
    revision_sources
    ON
        revision_sources.git_commit_hash = revisions.git_commit_hash AND
        revision_sources.patchset_hash = revisions.patchset_hash
ORDER BY
    tests_status_num DESC,
    checkouts_start_time DESC

SELECT

    IFNULL(ANY_VALUE(checkouts.git_repository_branch), "") AS git_repository_branch_str,
    SUBSTR(ANY_VALUE(checkouts.git_commit_hash), 0, 12) AS git_commit_hash_short,
    IFNULL(ANY_VALUE(checkouts.git_commit_name), "") AS git_commit_name_str,
    SUBSTR(ANY_VALUE(checkouts.patchset_hash), 0, 12) AS patchset_hash_short,
    IFNULL(CAST(ANY_VALUE(checkouts.start_time) AS STRING), "") AS start_time_str,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests_num,
    MAX((CASE tests.status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
        (CASE tests.waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS tests_status_num
FROM
    ${dataset}.checkouts AS checkouts
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.builds AS builds
    ON
        builds.checkout_id = checkouts.id AND
        IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
        IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.tests AS tests
    ON
        tests.build_id = builds.id AND
        tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
        tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND

        (${test_path:json} = "" OR

GROUP BY

ORDER BY
    tests_status_num DESC,
    ANY_VALUE(checkouts.start_time) DESC

SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    builds.id AS id,
    ANY_VALUE(builds.origin) AS origin,
    ANY_VALUE(builds.architecture) AS architecture,
    REGEXP_REPLACE(ANY_VALUE(builds.compiler), "^(.{48}).+$", "\\1â€¦") AS compiler,
    REGEXP_REPLACE(ANY_VALUE(builds.config_name), "^(.{48}).+$", "\\1â€¦") AS config_name,
    IFNULL(CAST(ANY_VALUE(builds.start_time) AS STRING), "") AS start_time_str,
    IFNULL(FORMAT_TIME("%H:%M:%E3S", TIME_ADD(TIME "00:00:00", INTERVAL CAST((ANY_VALUE(builds.duration) * 1000) AS INT64) MILLISECOND)), "") AS duration_str,
    ANY_VALUE(builds.comment) AS comment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT tests.id) AS tests_num,
    MAX((CASE tests.status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
        (CASE tests.waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6) AS tests_status_num
FROM ${dataset}.builds AS builds
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.tests AS tests
    ON
        tests.build_id = builds.id AND
        tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
        tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
        tests.path IS NOT NULL AND
        (${test_path:json} = "" OR
         tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
         STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
WHERE
    IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
    IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
GROUP BY
    builds.id
ORDER BY
    tests_status_num DESC,
    ANY_VALUE(builds.start_time) ASC

SELECT
    IF(${origin} = "%", "All", ${origin}) AS origin_param,
    IF(${build_architecture} = "%", "All", ${build_architecture}) AS build_architecture_param,
    IF(${build_config_name} = "%", "All", ${build_config_name}) AS build_config_name_param,
    tests.id,
    tests.origin,
    tests.path,
    tests.comment,
    builds.architecture,
    IFNULL(CAST(tests.start_time AS STRING), "") AS start_time_str,
    IFNULL(
        FORMAT_TIME("%H:%M:%E3S", TIME_ADD(TIME "00:00:00", INTERVAL CAST((tests.duration * 1000) AS INT64) MILLISECOND)),
        ""
    ) AS duration_str,
    (CASE status WHEN "ERROR" THEN 5 WHEN "FAIL" THEN 4 WHEN "PASS" THEN 3 WHEN "DONE" THEN 2 WHEN "SKIP" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -
        (CASE waived WHEN false THEN 0 WHEN true THEN 1 ELSE 2 END) * 6 AS status_num
FROM ${dataset}.tests
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.builds AS builds
    ON
        tests.build_id = builds.id AND
        IFNULL(builds.architecture LIKE ${build_architecture}, TRUE) AND
        IFNULL(builds.config_name LIKE ${build_config_name}, TRUE)
INNER JOIN
    ${dataset}.checkouts AS checkouts
    ON
        builds.checkout_id = checkouts.id
WHERE
    tests.start_time BETWEEN TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__from) AND TIMESTAMP_MILLIS($__to) AND
    tests.origin LIKE ${origin} AND
    (${test_path:json} = "" AND tests.path IS NOT NULL OR
     tests.path = ${test_path:json} OR
     STARTS_WITH(tests.path, ${test_path:json} || "."))
ORDER BY
    status_num DESC,
    tests.path ASC
